data.title: Monsters
authors: Contributors to Binding of Isaac: Rebirth Wiki
data.meta_description: Monsters refers to the many antagonistic creatures and entities the player will encounter throughout the game. Most monsters (with few exceptions) will damage Isaac by either touching him or shooting him with projectiles. Less frequently, monsters will spawn additional, lesser monsters, spread...
data.text:
Entity ID Description Frowning Gaper

10.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. They start out with their eyes closed, but when they gain line of sight with Isaac, their eyes open and they permanently move faster. Usually turns into a Pacer or with a small chance a Gusher upon death. Gaper

10.1 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Usually turns into a Pacer or a Gusher upon death. Flaming Gaper

10.2 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Usually turns into a Pacer or Gusher upon death. Rotten Gaper

10.3 Walks toward Isaac, dealing contact damage. Its behavior varies slightly depending on its facial expression. Gurgle

87.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage and periodically firing Ipecac shots at him; they are immune to this explosion, but other enemies are not. Can turn into a Splasher upon death. Crackle

87.1 Walks toward Isaac, dealing contact damage and spitting fireballs that create lines of fire in the cardinal directions on impact. Nulls

252.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Upon getting near Isaac, it will open its eyes, though its speed doesn't change. Fades into and out of visibility. Cyclopia

284.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage and leaving behind a short-lasting trail of damaging Red Creep. Occasionally shoots a blood shot towards Isaac. Blue Gaper

297.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Greed Gaper

299.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Wraith

807.0 Walks toward Isaac, dealing contact damage. They are invisible and can only be seen through the reflection they cast in the water, or the ripples they make as they walk. Deep Gaper

811.0 Emerges from the floor once all previous enemies have been killed, then proceeds to chase Isaac. Deals contact damage. Blurb

813.0 Walks slowly towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. After taking some damage or getting close to Isaac, it fires a chaotic burst of tears at him and chases him more quickly. Can turn into a Pacer or Gusher upon death. Level 2 Gaper

850.0 Walks towards Isaac, dealing a full Heart of contact damage. Splits into a Level 2 Horf and Level 2 Gusher upon death. Level 2 Horf

850.1 Slowly floats toward Isaac, spitting Small Maggots at him. Level 2 Gusher

850.2 Runs aimlessly around the room, spitting up Small Maggots. Twitchy

851.0 Alternates between walking towards and rapidly leaping at Isaac, dealing contact damage. Can leap to Isaac's current position, or where Isaac is heading, and can also leap away to dodge incoming fire. Dead Isaac

912.20 Summoned by Mother at the bottom of the arena, they walk upward (ignoring Isaac completely), and deal contact damage. Releases a burst of blood shots upon being killed by Mother, while she launches their corpses towards Isaac. Faceless

827.0 Wanders around the room, rarely firing a radial burst of six shots. Chases Isaac and fires shots more frequently after taking damage. Tainted Faceless

827.1 Wanders around the room, rarely firing a radial burst of six shots. Chases Isaac and fires shots very frequently after taking damage. Exorcist

832.0 Summons The Heretic before transforming into Fanatics. Fanatic

832.1 Transformed into from Exorcists. Chases Isaac and occasionally fires two purple, rotating shots. Candler

833.0 Flies around the room and propels itself by spawning flames. Dump

876.0 Slides toward Isaac, leaving a trail of slippery brown creep. After taking enough damage, its head slides off and quickly bounces around the room and its body spews out brown shots until it empties. Dump Head

876.1 Quickly slides toward Isaac, leaving a trail of slippery brown creep. Can spawn on its own or be created by a Dump after it takes enough damage. Gusher

11.0 Walks aimlessly around the room, occasionally firing a short-ranged blood shot. Pacer

11.1 Walks aimlessly around the room. Splasher

238.0 Walks aimlessly around the room, firing Ipecac shots in random directions. Black Globin's Body

280.0 Walks aimlessly around the room, occasionally spawning spiders. Horf

12.0 Stationary enemy that fires a medium-ranged blood shot at Isaac when he gets in range of them. Psychic Horf

248.0 Stationary enemy that fires a homing shot at Isaac when he gets in range of them. Sub Horf

812.0 Stationary enemy that spins and fires shots while being moved around or knocked back. Tainted Sub Horf

812.1 Will only shoot when hit. Takes heavy knockback and rotates when hit. Shoots a lot faster and has bigger projectiles than its normal variant. Necro

828.0 Stationary enemy that summons unlimited-ranged bones to attack Isaac. Fly

13.0 Hovers in place. Does not deal contact damage and is harmless, but can turn into Pooters if they stay around Poop. Attack Fly

18.0 Red fly that follows Isaac and deals contact damage. Moter

80.0 Follows Isaac, similar to Attack Flies. Deals contact damage. Splits into 2 Attack Flies upon death. Eternal Fly

96.0 Invulnerable fly that circles Corny Poop and various monsters. Deals contact damage. Turns into a vulnerable Attack Fly after the object or monster it circles is destroyed. Ring Fly

222.0 Gathers with any other Ring Flies in the room. These flies orbit around themselves while following Isaac. Deals contact damage. Dart Fly

256.0 Flies towards Isaac and attempts to predict his movements. Deals contact damage. Swarm

281.0 Follows Isaac in large, tightly-clustered groups and deals contact damage. Hush Fly

296.0 Gathers with other Hush Flies to form certain patterns. If spawned by Hush, can chase Isaac or orbit Hush. Deals contact damage. Willo

808.0 Flies in a circle around Isaac (in formation with other Willos if available), keeping an exact distance away from him. One Willo at a time will occasionally light up and fire a shot at Isaac. Army Fly

868.0 Chases Isaac, moving along the cardinal directions. Forms a line with other Army Flies in the room. Deals contact damage. Ultra Famine Fly

951.11 Charges at Isaac at a delay. Deals contact damage. Spawned by Ultra Famine. Ultra Pestilence Fly

951.21 Flies in swarms around Ultra Pestilence, blocking shots and dealing contact damage. Fly Bomb

819.0 Flies toward Isaac, circling around him as it does. Turn into a tiny Bomb upon death. Eternal Fly Bomb

819.1 Orbits Boom Flies spawned by The Horny Boys. Once its Boom Fly has been killed, turns into a tiny Bomb. Sucker

61.0 Flies slowly towards Isaac, exploding into 4 shots in the cardinal directions upon death. Spit

61.1 Flies slowly towards Isaac, firing an Ipecac shot towards Isaac upon death. Ink

61.3 Flies slowly towards Isaac. Fires four shots in the ordinal directions and leaves a puddle of slowing Black Creep upon death. Soul Sucker

61.2 Flies slowly towards Isaac. Spawns a vortex that fires four Brimstone beams in the cardinal directions upon death. Mama Fly

61.4 Flies more-or-less away from Isaac, occasionally plopping on the ground to plant a Pustule. Upon death, they spawn a group of Small Maggots. Bulb

61.5 Flies in erratic, angled movements toward Isaac if his active item has charges; on contact, they drain up to 2 charges, but never deal contact damage. If he has no active item, or no charges, they wander around the room aimlessly. Bloodfly

61.6 Spawned only after a Pustule bursts. Flies in erratic, angled movements toward Isaac. Fires four blood shots in the cardinal directions upon death. Tainted Sucker

61.7 Flies slowly towards Isaac. Upon death, fires a radial burst of six blood shots that each also fires a radial burst of six blood shots. Pooter

14.0 Slowly drifts toward Isaac, occasionally firing a single blood shot at him. Does not deal contact damage. Super Pooter

14.1 Slowly drifts toward Isaac, occasionally firing two blood shots in a V-formation at him. Does not deal contact damage. Tainted Pooter

14.2 Slowly drifts toward Isaac, occasionally firing four blood shots at him that split into two smaller ones when they hit a wall or obstacle. Clotty

15.0 Randomly wanders around the room, firing 4 blood shots in the cardinal directions. Clot

15.1 Randomly wanders around the room, firing 4 tar shots in the ordinal directions. I.Blob

15.2 Randomly wanders around the room, firing 8 shots in all directions. Grilled Clotty

15.3 Quickly and randomly wanders around the room, firing four flame shots in the cardinal directions at a slight angle. Cloggy

872.0 Randomly wanders around the room, firing four curved brown shots in the cardinal directions. These shots alternate between rotating clockwise and counterclockwise with each shot. Mulligan

16.0 Walks around the room, avoiding Isaac. Upon death, spawns several flies, which can be Flies, Attack Flies, and/or Pooters. Can self-detonate and launch four projectiles in the cardinal directions while still releasing flies. Mulligoon

16.1 Walks around the room, avoiding Isaac. Upon death, spawns a Troll Bomb and fires four shots in the ordinal directions. Can self-detonate, spawn a Troll bomb, and launch eight projectiles in all directions. Mulliboom

16.2 Chases Isaac and explodes upon death or upon touching Isaac. The explosion deals a half-heart of damage instead of the regular full heart. Hive

22.0 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Attack Flies if he gets close. Spawns a large number of flies on death, which can be Flies, Attack Flies, and/or Pooters. Drowned Hive

22.1 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Drowned Chargers if he gets close. Spawns 0-2 Drowned Chargers upon death. Holy Mulligan

22.2 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Angelic Baby (small) if he gets close. Spawns 1-2 Embryos upon death. Tainted Mulligan

22.3 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning 6 Ring Flies if he gets close. Spawns a plethora of fly enemies upon death. Nest

205.0 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Spiders if he gets close. Spawns a Big Spider or Trite upon death. Leper

310.0 Alternating between walking towards and running away from Isaac. Releases a Leper Flesh each time it takes enough damage. At low health, constantly chases Isaac and leaves behind damaging red creep. Spawns a Leper Flesh and Gusher upon death. Leper Flesh

310.1 Floats slowly toward Isaac and fires a predictive projectile at him upon death. Prey

817.0 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Small Leeches if he gets close. Spawns 3 Small Leeches upon death. Mullighoul

817.1 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac and spawning Willos if he gets close. Spawns 1-2 Willos upon death. Bouncer

822.0 Wanders around the room, avoiding Isaac. If Isaac stays close to one for long enough, it inflates and starts chasing him, gaining a chance to deflect shots and causing it to explode into lingering blood shots on death. Gas Dwarf

874.0 Chases Isaac, periodically coughing up gas clouds. On death, fires an explosive shot that can detonate gas clouds it hits. Danny

820.0 Walks toward Isaac and spits chaotic bursts of rocks at him, some of which may be Rock Spiders. Coal Boy

820.1 Walks toward Isaac and spits hot coals at him, some of which may be Coal Spiders. Blaster

821.0 Slowly wanders around and occasionally shoots Fly Bombs at Isaac. Maggot

21.0 Aimlessly moves around the room, dealing contact damage. Charger

23.0 Slowly moves around the room, charging at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. My Shadow

23.0.1 Charges at enemies when in its line of sight, dealing contact damage. Will always spawn friendly via My Shadow. Drowned Charger

23.1 Slowly moves around the room, charging at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Explodes into four blood shots in the ordinal directions upon death. Dank Charger

23.2 Slowly moves around the room, launching itself at Isaac if he gets in its line of sight. Bounces off of walls and leaves a trail of slowing Black Creep while charging. Carrion Princess

23.3 Slowly moves around the room, charging at Isaac when he lines up diagonally with it. Can only be damaged by hitting its tail. Small Leech

810.0 Chases Isaac continuously, not stopping at walls. Able to swim over gaps. Small Maggot

853.0 Slowly crawls toward Isaac, dealing contact damage. Level 2 Charger

855.0 Slowly moves around the room, charging at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Can slowly change its trajectory while charging. Elleech

855.1 Slowly moves around the room. After Isaac gets in its line of sight, continuously charges at him in the closest cardinal direction. Blood Puppy

802.0 Quickly moves around the room, attacking and charging at other monsters and Isaac when they get in its line of sight. Spitty

31.0 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally firing a single blood shot forward. Tainted Spitty

31.1 Slowly moves around the room, firing chaotic bursts of blood shots in all directions and occasionally spitting a line of blood shots in the direction it's facing. Fires two rotating rings of blood shots upon death. Conjoined Spitty

243.0 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally firing a blood shot from both ends of its body. Globin

24.0 Chases Isaac, dealing a full heart of contact damage. Upon taking enough damage, it collapses into a pile of goo, which can be killed. Will regenerate after a short period of time if not killed quickly. Gazing Globin

24.1 Quickly chases Isaac, dealing a full heart of contact damage. Upon taking enough damage, it collapses into a pile of goo, which will slide away from Isaac and can be killed. Will regenerate after a short period of time if not killed quickly. Dank Globin

24.2 Chases Isaac, dealing a full heart of contact damage. Upon taking enough damage, it collapses into a pile of goo, spawns a Spider, and leaves a puddle of slowing Black Creep. Will regenerate after a short time if not killed quickly. Leaves another puddle of Black Creep upon death. Cursed Globin

24.3 Chases Isaac, dealing a full heart of contact damage. Upon taking enough damage, it collapses into 1-2 piles of goo, each of which can be killed and regenerate after a short period of time if not killed quickly. These goo piles have less health the more times the Cursed Globin splits. Black Globin

278.0 Chases Isaac, dealing a full heart of contact damage and launching Spiders towards Isaac whenever it takes damage. Spawns a Spider, a Black Globin's Head, and a Black Globin's Body upon death. Clickety Clack

889.0 Walks towards Isaac and turn into a pile of bones when killed. Regenerates a few seconds after killed. Will only despawn if all Clickety Clacks in the room are killed. Gasbag

856.0 Occasionally summons Army Flies to chase Isaac. Is surrounded by a ring of toxic gas that hurts Isaac if he stands in it for too long. Cohort

857.0 Acts similarly to Monstro, hopping towards Isaac and can either spit a large projectile towards Isaac that bursts into 8 smaller projectiles or cough up a burst of arcing projectiles and a pile of Globin goo. Spawns 4 piles of Globin goo upon death. Boom Fly

25.0 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Explodes upon death. Red Boom Fly

25.1 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Creates a ring of 6 blood shots upon death. Drowned Boom Fly

25.2 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Upon death, explodes and fires four blood shots in the cardinal directions. Also has a chance to spawn a Drowned Charger upon death. Dragon Fly

25.3.0 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Upon death, creates four lines of fire in the cardinal directions; the fire nearly spans the length of an entire normal-sized room. Dragon Fly X

25.3.1 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Upon death, creates four lines of fire in the ordinal directions; the fire nearly spans the length of an entire normal-sized room. Bone Fly

25.4 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Fires bones at Isaac if he lines up with it in the cardinal directions. Fires a radial burst of 3 bones upon death. Sick Boom Fly

25.5 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage and trailing poisonous gas. Upon death, explodes into a gas cloud and fires a ring of 6 green shots. Tainted Boom Fly

25.6 Flies across the room in straight diagonal lines, dealing contact damage. Upon death, it glows brightly, warning that it is about to explode; this explosion sends 4 lines of further explosions in the cardinal directions, which span the length of the room. Maw

26.0 Slowly floats towards Isaac, firing a blood shot at him when he is in their range. Red Maw

26.1 Floats quickly towards Isaac and releases 4 blood shots in the cardinal directions upon death. Psychic Maw

26.2 Slowly floats towards Isaac, firing homing shots at him when he is in their range. Spawns with an Eternal Fly orbiting around it. Host

27.0 Stationary enemy that is normally invulnerable. Raises its head up when Isaac gets close, revealing a fleshy stem that can be damaged. Upon raising its head, it will fire 3 blood shots in a spread and lower its head again. Red Host

27.1 Stationary enemy that can be damaged even when its head is lowered. Fire 5 spread blood shots when it raises its head. Hard Host

27.3 Stationary enemy that is normally invulnerable. Raises its head up when Isaac gets close, revealing a fleshy stem that can be damaged. Shortly after raising its head, it slams its head down and fires a rock wave towards Isaac. Mobile Host

204.0 Acts like the Host, but follows Isaac and deals contact damage. Flesh Mobile Host

247.0 Acts like the Red Host, but follows Isaac and deals contact damage. Floast

859.0 Floats diagonally around the room and is normally invulnerable. When Isaac gets close, reveals a fleshy stem that can be damaged and fires 3 blood shots in an angle at him before hiding its stem again. Mushroom

300.0 Stationary enemy that occasionally pops up and fires four shots in the cardinal or diagonal directions. Takes less damage while its head is down. Hopper

29.0 Slowly hops around the room, doing contact damage. Can turn into a Flaming Hopper by jumping into Fire Places or other fires. Eggy

29.2 Hops aimlessly around the room, spawning slowing white creep wherever it hops. Spawns a group of Swarm Spiders upon death. Tainted Hopper

29.3 Jumps and twirls around the room, shooting 4 rings of projectiles that increase in size with each shot. Leaper

34.0 Hops around the room, doing contact damage. Occasionally jumps high into the air, dropping down onto Isaac's position while firing 4 blood shots in the cardinal directions. Sticky Leaper

34.1 Hops around the room, dealing contact damage. Occasionally jumps high into the air, dropping down onto Isaac's position while creating a chaotic burst of tar shots in all directions and a puddle of slowing black creep. Flaming Hopper

54.0 Quickly hops around the room, doing contact damage. Covers a larger distance than the regular Hopper. Trite

29.1 Quickly leaps towards Isaac and deals contact damage. Ragling

246.0 Quickly leaps towards Isaac and deals contact damage. Randomly shoots two purple shots that orbit around it. Rag Man's Ragling

246.1 Quickly leaps towards Isaac and deals contact damage. Randomly shoots two purple shots that orbit around it. Blister

303.0 Slowly hops towards Isaac, occasionally spawning a Dark Ball. Spawns a Sack upon death. Boil

30.0 Stationary enemy that decreases in size when hit, but regenerates to its full size until fully destroyed. Fires multiple short-ranged blood projectiles in random directions when fully swollen. Gut

30.1 Stationary enemy that decreases in size when hit, but regenerates to its full size until fully destroyed. Fires Ipecac shots in random directions when fully swollen. Sack

30.2 Stationary enemy that decreases in size when hit, but regenerates to its full size until fully destroyed. Occasionally spawns Spiders when fully swollen. Blue Boil

298.0 Stationary enemy that decreases in size when hit, but regenerates to its full size until fully destroyed. Fires 1-3 blood shots towards Isaac when fully swollen. Gush

309.0 Stationary, harmless enemy that continually creates slowing black creep. Pustule

861.0 Slowly increases in size over time, spawning Small Maggots and damaging red creep depending on its size upon death. If it grows to full size, it transforms into a Bloodfly. Walking Boil

88.0 Does not shrink or regenerate. Walks around aimlessly and fires multiple short-ranged blood projectiles in random directions. Walking Gut

88.1 Does not shrink or regenerate. Walks around aimlessly and fires Ipecac shots in random directions. Walking Sack

88.2 Does not shrink or regenerate. Walks around aimlessly and occasionally spawns Spiders. Brain

32.0 Slowly crawls around the room, leaving a trail of Red Creep. Black Globin's Head

279.0 Slides towards Isaac, leaving a trail of damaging Red Creep. Festering Guts

831.20 Spawned by Gutted Fatties, Festering Guts randomly slide around the room and occasionally spawn a Charger. Poison Mind

301.0 Slowly crawls/ floats around the room diagonally, leaving a trail of damaging green creep. Explodes upon death. Pon

840.0 Hops around the room, leaving damaging red creep wherever it lands. Upon death, its associated Brainless Knight dies with it. Gyro

824.0 Rolls around like a wheel. Charges at Isaac when he is in line of sight, bouncing off of walls and obstacles as it does. Grilled Gyro

824.1 Rolls around like a wheel. Charges at Isaac when he is in line of sight, bouncing off of walls and obstacles and creating fires behind itself as it does. Mr. Maw

35.0 Walks towards Isaac and attacks by launching its head towards him. Turns into a Maw or Gusher upon death depending on the killed body segment. Occasionally separates at will. Mr. Red Maw

35.2 Walks towards Isaac and attacks by launching its head towards him. Turns into a Red Maw or Gusher upon death depending on the killed body segment. Occasionally separates at will. Swinger

216.0 Slowly moves towards Isaac as its head swings around its base. Upon death, spawns a Maw or a Globin depending on which part is killed. Mr. Mine

311.0 Can only appear in pits. Attempts to launch itself at Isaac if he comes near. Occasionally burrows and pops up in another pit, and fires six shots in all directions upon death. Baby

38.0 Slowly floats towards Isaac and fires a blood shot at him. Occasionally teleports and reappears elsewhere. Angelic Baby

38.1.0 Slowly floats towards Isaac and fires three spread shots. Occasionally teleports and reappears elsewhere. Angelic Baby (small)

38.1.1 Slowly floats towards Isaac and fires a blood shot at him. Occasionally teleports and reappears elsewhere. Can only be spawned by Holy Mulligans. Wrinkly Baby

38.3 Dashes towards Isaac at high speed and fires three blood shots in his direction once stopped. Imp

259.0 Slowly drifts towards Isaac, frequently firing 5 blood shots in quick succession towards him. Tries to avoid Isaac's shots and occasionally teleports and reappears elsewhere. Unborn

860.0 Floats quickly towards Isaac, and occasionally teleports to another position near him. Baby Begotten

883.0 Floats toward Isaac, avoiding his shots. After getting close, fires a short Brimstone laser in the closest cardinal direction and propels itself away from him. Vis

39.0 Randomly wanders around the room. Pauses to charge and fire a Brimstone laser when Isaac gets in its line of sight. Double Vis

39.1 Randomly wanders around the room. Pauses to charge and fire a Brimstone laser which fires from both sides when Isaac gets in its line of sight. Chubber

39.2 Randomly wanders around the room. Pauses to fire a Charger that deals one heart of damage when Isaac gets in its line of sight. The Charger is invulnerable, blocks Isaac's tears, has limited range, and flies back to the Chubber. Scarred Double Vis

39.3 Randomly wanders around the room. Pauses to charge and fire a Brimstone laser which fires from all four cardinal sides when Isaac gets in its line of sight. Vis Versa

836.0 Randomly wanders around the room. Pauses to charge and fire a homing Brimstone laser when Isaac gets in its line of sight. Evis

865.0 Randomly wanders around the room. Launches a string of guts when Isaac gets close to it, which it uses to pull Isaac toward itself. Guts

40.0 Attaches itself to a wall or obstacle and rolls around it. Scarred Guts

40.1 Attaches itself to a wall or obstacle and rolls around it, leaving a trail of damaging Red Creep. Slog

40.2 Attaches itself to a wall or obstacle and rolls around it, charging at Isaac when he is in sight. Cyst

862.0 Attaches itself to a wall or obstacle and rolls around it, regularly firing blood shots at Isaac. Knight

41.0 Moves erratically around the room and charges towards Isaac when in line of sight. Can only be damaged from behind. Selfless Knight

41.1 Moves erratically around the room and charges towards Isaac very quickly when in line of sight. Can only be damaged from behind. Loose Knight

41.2 Moves erratically around the room, charges toward Isaac when in line of sight. When its health is depleted, it turns into a Brainless Knight and a Pon. Brainless Knight

41.3 Alternates between running around the room along the cardinal directions and aimlessly walking in circles. Charges at Isaac when in line of sight. Dies when its corresponding Pon dies. Black Knight

41.4 Moves erratically around the room, charges toward Isaac when in line of sight. Unleashes waves of fire in all cardinal directions upon charging into an obstacle. Shots that hit it from the front are deflected back at Isaac. Floating Knight

254.0 Behaves like the Knight but slower, and can fly over all obstacles. Bone Knight

283.0 Moves erratically around the room, charges toward Isaac when in line of sight, and leaves behind a short-lasting trail of damaging Red Creep. Can only be damaged from behind. Whipper

834.0 Runs around the room, sprinting at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight and lashing at him when it gets close. Snapper

834.1 Runs around the room, sprinting at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight and throwing out its whip when he gets in range. Flagellant

834.2 Runs around the room. When Isaac gets in its line of sight, continuously chases him and lashes its whip, occasionally deflecting Isaacs shots. Dople

53.0 Mirrors Isaac's movements and fires blood shots at the same time as Isaac. Can be damaged by spikes. Evil Twin

53.1 Mirrors Isaac's movements and fires three spread blood shots at the same time as Isaac. Can fly over obstacles. Leech

55.0 Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Kamikaze Leech

55.1 Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Explodes upon death. Holy Leech

55.2 Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Explodes upon death. Spawns with an Eternal Fly circling it, which instantly dies when the Holy Leech explodes. Adult Leech

854.0 Wanders around the room, quickly charging at Isaac when he lines up horizontally with him and releasing a ring of blood shots upon colliding with a wall. After taking a certain amount of damage, burrows into the ground and reappears by falling above Isaac, releasing another ring of blood shots and only performing this behavior once. Lump

56.0 Fires 3 spread blood shots at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Will burrow underground and reappear elsewhere after firing. Tar Boy

307.0 Fires a short-ranged spray of shots that leave behind slowing Black Creep. Occasionally burrows underground and reappears under any pools of black creep in the room. If Isaac stands on the Creep, the Tar Boy can fire shots straight upwards out of the Creep underneath Isaac/ send out a tentacle underneath Isaac. MemBrain

57.0 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and firing 8 large blood shots in all directions. Splits into 2 Brains upon death. Mama Guts

57.1 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and firing 8 large blood shots in all directions. Splits into 2 Guts upon death. Dead Meat

57.2 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and firing 8 large blood shots in all directions that bounce off the walls. Splits into 2 Cysts upon death. Dinga

223.0 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping to spawn Dips or fire 8 Brown shots in all directions. Splits 2 Squirts upon death. Mega Clotty

282.0 Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and either firing 6 blood shots in all directions, leaving a puddle of Red Creep, or spawning a Clotty or a collapsed Globin. Splits into two Clotties upon death. Para-Bite

58.0 Moves towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Can burrow underground and reappear elsewhere. Scarred Para-Bite

58.1 Moves towards Isaac, dealing contact damage and firing a short-range blood shot at him. Can burrow underground and reappear elsewhere. Fred

59.0 Hops out of the ground and burrows elsewhere, firing 4 blood shots in the cardinal directions. Occasionally fires red Ipecac shots at Isaac. Eye

60.0 Slowly turns towards Isaac and fires a Technology laser at Isaac if he stands still or is too slow. Bloodshot Eye

60.1 Slowly turns towards Isaac and fires a Brimstone beam at Isaac if he stands still or is too slow. Holy Eye

60.2 Rapidly summons several beams of light around Isaac every few seconds. Embryo

77.0 Aimlessly hops around the room, dealing contact damage. Spider

85.0 Erratically moves around the room. If Isaac gets close to it, it chases him, trying to deal contact damage. Big Spider

94.0 Erratically moves around the room. If Isaac gets close to it, it chases him, trying to deal contact damage. Spawns two Spiders upon death. Strider

814.0 Erratically swims around the room. If it sees Isaac, it chases him, trying to deal contact damage. Rock Spider

818.0 Slowly crawls around the room. If it sees Isaac, it crawls at him, trying to deal contact damage. Turns into a Spider upon death. Turns into a Coal Spider if it touches fire. Tinted Rock Spider

818.1 Quickly crawls around the room. If it sees Isaac, it crawls at him, trying to deal contact damage. Turns into a Soul Heart upon death. Can only spawn by breaking tinted rocks on Mines or Ashpit. Coal Spider

818.2 Quickly crawls around the room. If it sees Isaac, it crawls at him, trying to deal contact damage. Turns into a hot coal upon death that blocks shots and deals contact damage, but can be destroyed. Swarm Spider

884.0 Very erratically hops toward Isaac in large groups, dealing contact damage. Keeper

86.0 Hops around the room, firing 2 blood shots in a V formation at Isaac. Upon damaging Isaac, Isaac drops 2 coins on the ground but loses 3. Buttlicker

89.0 Can start attached to other Buttlickers and erratically moves around the room, similar to Larry Jr.. Butt Slicker

878.0 Moves erratically around the room unless attached to another Butt Slicker. Grouped Butt Slickers drag themselves towards Isaac, and when an individual is killed they leave black creep, and shoot out black projectiles. The amount of projectiles released and the size of the pool of Black Creep is determined by the amount of Butt Slickers attached. Hanger

90.0 Floats around the room, firing 3 spread blood shots at Isaac. Upon damaging Isaac, Isaac drops 2 coins on the ground but loses 3. Spawns with an Eternal Fly circling around it. Swarmer

91.0 Slowly floats around the room, spawning several Attack Flies. Spawns Pooters upon taking damage. Spawns a Boom Fly upon death. Mask + Heart

93.0 The Mask is invulnerable and moves around erratically, charging at Isaac when he lines up with it. The Heart avoids Isaac and fires 4 blood shots in the cardinal directions when Isaac gets near. Killing the Heart will automatically kill the Mask. Mask II + 1/2 Heart

93.1 The Mask is invulnerable and moves around erratically, charging at Isaac when he lines up with it. The Heart avoids Isaac and fires 4 blood shots in the ordinal directions when Isaac gets near. Killing the Heart will automatically kill the Mask. If there are more than one 1/2 Heart in the room, they will fire blood shots between each other. Baby Long Legs

206.0 Runs away from Isaac and frequently spawns Spiders. Small Baby Long Legs

206.1 Runs away from Isaac and occasionally spawns Sacks. Crazy Long Legs
